title: John Scofield - 1995-09-02 Artpark, Lewiston, NY [24-96]
description:
John Scofield
Artpark
Lewiston, NY
September 2, 1995

24 bit version 

Taper: Bigdaddybflo
Gear: No gear was listed on the tape, but knowing this guy I think it's safe to assume DSM6/PC > WMD6
Transferred & mastered by }{eywood
Lineage: Maxell XLII 90 (M) > Optimus SCT-57 playback deck > Adobe Audition 1.5 (recording at 24/96, normalization, splits & fades, flac 8)

no EQ or other invasive processing was used on this tape.  This is how it sounded, which is great.  

All but one of the song titles were stated at the show.

02 Out of the City
03 band intros
